description:
Watch The Heavy Heavy perform "Feel" in The Current studio
Support The Current: https://support.mpr.org/youtube 

While in the Twin Cities for a show at First Avenue in Minneapolis, The Heavy Heavy visited The Current studio to play songs from their debut album "One Of A Kind."

Watch the performance of "Feel" above.

Musicians
Will Turner – vocals, guitar
Georgie Fuller – vocals, keyboards
Frank Fogden – guitar, keyboards
Thomas Holder – bass
Joe Bordenaro – drums
